- cs.SD (Sound): This sub-category deals with audio data, which is not directly related to this paper. However, the use of colloquial slang in the dataset may be related to sound-based analysis of language.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): This sub-category deals with the social impact of computing and technology, which is relevant to this paper as it focuses on the impact of tobacco use on society.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): This sub-category deals with machine learning methods, which are used in this paper for text classification.
